_sText:
This map was a short project. I built everything in 3 days. It is an xc map with 9 stages. The game Q.U.B.E. inspired me so i tried to copy the design. Here the original game: http://store.steampowered.com/app/203730/

Features of the map:

• 9 stages  
• Q.U.B.E. design  
• Custom radar  
• Anti-Scout  
• Strafe Longjumps up to 250 units  
• Time controlled stages  
• Boosters  

All blocks are individual. Textures are all selfmade or made by valve.

Have fun with this little xc map :)

Dotty
